50|$|The Queen Fabiola International <b>Carillon</b> Competition was {{established}} by the school in 1987. Every five years, carillonneurs from the world over converge in Mechelen {{to compete in the}} most prestigious <b>carillon</b> competition in history. The school also organizes <b>carillon</b> composition contests and publishes works for <b>carillon,</b> campanological literature, and <b>carillon</b> methods.|$|R
